{"tid":856733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想同大家分享一個全球性既組織，Avaaz","createTime":"2018-10-10T17:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T17:40:54.000Z","uid":115847,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1c25f6da02fc17c1724c7c2f6eedf8828e0ecbaf","tid":856733,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:39:03.000Z","msg":"- Avaaz 是國際線上倡議社群，藉助全球公民力量影響全球決策。-<br />\n<a href=\"https://secure.avaaz.org/page/ct/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.avaaz.org%2Fpage%2Fct%2F&d=xflcCrgVt7Tsunh6gOrJRAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=69975712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://secure.avaaz.org/page/ct/</a><br />\n<br />\n大概subscribe左佢2,3年，間唔中就會send email來，<br />\n內容係來至世界各地唔同既倡議，<br />\n好似咁 v<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCCn5S9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCCn5S9.png&h=c17fd95a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCyZoFo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCyZoFo.png&h=19377e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網頁version: <br />\n<a href=\"https://secure.avaaz.org/campaign/ct/iceland_stop_the_whale_slaughter/?tANdLib&amp;v=500570591&amp;cl=15074876552&amp;_checksum=d307f54c7373772f7fcb8923b04967d40b0ac3ae781c95099a6ee9e8722225f3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.avaaz.org%2Fcampaign%2Fct%2Ficeland_stop_the_whale_slaughter%2F%3FtANdLib%26v%3D500570591%26cl%3D15074876552%26_checksum%3Dd307f54c7373772f7fcb8923b04967d40b0ac3ae781c95099a6ee9e8722225f3&d=xflcCrgVt7Tsunh6gOrJRAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d202a331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://secure.avaaz.org/campaign/ct/iceland_stop_the_whale_slaughter/?tANdLib&amp;v=500570591&amp;cl=15074876552&amp;_checksum=d307f54c7373772f7fcb8923b04967d40b0ac3ae781c95099a6ee9e8722225f3</a><br />\n<br />\n如果認同佢地既話，就只需要&quot;噤&quot; [立刻連署]～<br />\n當佢地儲夠一定連署既人數後就會向相關組織，政府施壓，<br />\n從而達到佢地期望既結果。<br />\n<br />\n呢到係佢地過去&quot;成功&quot;既例子 ~<br />\n<a href=\"https://secure.avaaz.org/page/ct/highlights/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.avaaz.org%2Fpage%2Fct%2Fhighlights%2F&d=xflcCrgVt7Tsunh6gOrJRAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=354600d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://secure.avaaz.org/page/ct/highlights/</a><br />\n<br />\n想參與既話填個email，&quot;噤&quot;個制就得（當然每個case都要經過自己既分析)。<br />\n<br />\n最後，只希望大家唔好俾想變好既心死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n分享完畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacb8a036326f67c19fef2636377c7c633f85006","tid":856733,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:40:34.000Z","msg":"可以一試"},{"pid":"e399ac3edc2afc4b149a2f0eb0169724a5f19c61","tid":856733,"uid":30882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T17:40:54.000Z","msg":"睇錯性組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}